# 1Password CLI session gate (agents + operators)

1. **Canonical SSOT:** [docs/ONEPASSWORD_CLI_SESSION_GATE_SSOT.md](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/ONEPASSWORD_CLI_SESSION_GATE_SSOT.md) — **mandatory** for every **private repo** (this repo + consumers) before **`op read`**, **`op item`**, **`op run`** with **`op://`**, or **`CLOUDFLARE_AI_GATEWAY_OP_REF`** resolution.

1a. **Automation-first (workstations):** Before defaulting to interactive **§1**, confirm [ONEPASSWORD_CLI_SESSION_GATE_SSOT.md](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/ONEPASSWORD_CLI_SESSION_GATE_SSOT.md) **§3.1** — **`OP_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_TOKEN`**, **`with-op-service-account-env.sh`** / **`configure-op-service-account-env.sh`**, Keychain/libsecret sync, **`op run --env-file=`**, or **`credential-manager`** — are not already the correct path. Service accounts satisfy **`op read`** without **`op signin`**.

2. **Interactive shells (when unattended token is absent):** Do **not** assume **`op`** works because the **1Password app** is unlocked. Order: **`eval "$(op signin)"`** → operator completes vendor login → **`op whoami`** succeeds **in the same shell** that will run the script.

3. **Before suggesting or running** any script that touches **`op`**: if **`OP_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_TOKEN`** is not in use, run **`./scripts/op-ensure-session.sh`** (or confirm **`op whoami`**) in **that** shell; if it fails, use **§1** in [ONEPASSWORD_CLI_SESSION_GATE_SSOT.md](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/ONEPASSWORD_CLI_SESSION_GATE_SSOT.md). If **`op whoami`** succeeds but a resolver still **MISS**es, classify **vault field / ACL / Worker secret** (e.g. **`./scripts/diagnose-p0-op-materialization.sh`**) — do **not** attribute that to a “broken **`op`** session” or loop blindly on **`op read`** errors.

4. **CI / headless:** **`OP_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_TOKEN`** only — no interactive **`op signin`**; document in repo workflow.

5. **Cross-repo:** consumer repos that ship **`op`**-backed scripts **must** link **ONEPASSWORD_CLI_SESSION_GATE_SSOT** per [docs/CONSUMER_SSOT_BACKLINK_MINIMUM.md](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/CONSUMER_SSOT_BACKLINK_MINIMUM.md) item **8**.

6. **Which 1Password surface?** Do **not** expect the Cursor **plugin** or **`1Password.op-vscode`** to perform **`op item` CRUD** or **`op run`**. For full **`op`** capabilities + **`credential-manager`** from scripts, read [CURSOR_1PASSWORD_DEVELOPER_VAULT_2026-04-27.md](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/CURSOR_1PASSWORD_DEVELOPER_VAULT_2026-04-27.md) **§ Three-surface capability matrix** and **§ Consolidation direction** (Rust façade in **`credential-manager`**, not perpetual one-off bash); keep **`op whoami`** in the **same** shell as the automation.

7. **Wrappers and Rust binaries:** **`credential-manager`** or any tool that invokes **`op`** as a subprocess **inherits** the delegated session of the **parent** shell. Run **`eval "$(op signin)"`** (or **`OP_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_TOKEN`**) → **`op whoami`** **before** `./scripts/with-op-session.sh …` **or** the Rust binary **in that same terminal**; **`with-op-session.sh`** optionally runs **`scripts/op-ensure-session.sh`** for Touch ID parity. Escalating to a **fresh** subprocess without **`op`** env (daemon, disjoint Agent shell) is **invalid** unless you inject **`OP_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_TOKEN`**.
8. **`SdkSecrets::resolve`:** **`credential-manager`** **`OnePasswordSdkShape::sdk_secrets().resolve("op://…")`** is **`op read`** — same gate as rules **1–3** / **7**; canonical prose **[ONEPASSWORD_CLI_SESSION_GATE_SSOT.md](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/ONEPASSWORD_CLI_SESSION_GATE_SSOT.md) §5**. CI uses a **fake `op`** on **`PATH`** in **`tests/sdk_secrets_op_read_fake_op.rs`** (Unix); that does **not** remove the need for **§1–3** when running against a real vault.
9. **OP inventory suite:** after **§1–3**, operators may run **`./scripts/op-ssot-developer-cloudflare-inventory-suite.sh`** (canonical + fuzzy + **full-vault** **`deep-verify-cloudflare-tokens`** + optional sibling **`credential-manager`** fake-`op` test). **`OP_SSOT_INVENTORY_SUITE_SKIP_DEEP_VERIFY=1`** skips the long deep phase; **`OP_SSOT_INVENTORY_SUITE_OFFLINE=1`** runs **only** the Rust test when **`op`** is unavailable — **[ONEPASSWORD_CLI_SESSION_GATE_SSOT.md](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/ONEPASSWORD_CLI_SESSION_GATE_SSOT.md) §4**. **`./scripts/close-developer-vault-alignment-loop.sh`** runs that **offline** phase **first** (Phase **A**), then live **`vault-alignment-audit`** (Phase **B**) — **[ONEPASSWORD_CLI_SESSION_GATE_SSOT.md](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/ONEPASSWORD_CLI_SESSION_GATE_SSOT.md) §5.1** (fake **`op`** ≠ vault TSV).

10. **Title ↔ Cloudflare token NAME:** run **`./scripts/run-op-vault-alignment-audit.sh`** (optional **`--with-introspection`**) — **not** bare **`op-developer-cloudflare-vault-standardize.sh vault-alignment-audit`** from Agent-only docs. **`lib-op-shell-session.sh`** **`repo_op_prepare_cli_session_mcp_compatible`** defaults to **interactive** **`op-ensure-session`** (desktop / Touch ID) when **`op whoami`** is cold on a workstation (**not** **`CI`**, not **`OP_ENSURE_SESSION_NON_INTERACTIVE`**, not **`OP_INTERACTIVE_OP_UNLOCK=0`**). **`PROBE_HTTP_MAP`** paths: **`config/cloudflare-vault-alignment-probes.txt`** — **[TOKEN_CREATION_CHECKLIST_SSOT.md](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/TOKEN_CREATION_CHECKLIST_SSOT.md) §0.0c**, **[MCP_AND_CLOUDFLARE_VERIFICATION_HUB_SSOT.md](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/MCP_AND_CLOUDFLARE_VERIFICATION_HUB_SSOT.md) §1b**.

11. **Backup before vault writes:** **`./scripts/backup-op-vault-snapshot.sh`** (metadata and optional full JSON tree) and **`close-developer-vault-alignment-loop.sh`** pre-apply snapshots — **[ONEPASSWORD_CLI_SESSION_GATE_SSOT.md](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/ONEPASSWORD_CLI_SESSION_GATE_SSOT.md) §5.2**. Fully unattended strict path: **`OP_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_TOKEN`** + **`OP_VAULT_AUTOMATION_STRICT=1`** + explicit plaintext-backup ack.
12. **Unattended readiness gate:** prefer **`./scripts/with-op-service-account-env.sh python3 ./scripts/token-rotation-readiness-gate.py --non-interactive`** for repeatable non-mutating checks that fail closed on unresolved rows; normalize only explicit non-rotation artifacts in **`config/token-rotation-readiness-ignore-titles.txt`** and exclude **`Service Account Auth Token:*`** from Cloudflare-token defect counts; enforce script QA with **`./scripts/verify-python-security-toolchain.sh`**.
